OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Emma
OL,7,FSweeney reports from Manchester
OL,8,FCentral Mosque
OL,10,FA man has been arrested after two men
OL,11,Fallegedly entered a Mosque "carrying
OL,12,Fmultiple weapons" including an axe and
OL,13,Fa hammer as people worshipped during
OL,14,FRamadan.
OL,16,FPolice were called to Manchester
OL,17,FCentral Mosque, in the Victoria Park
OL,18,Farea in the south of the city, at
OL,19,Faround 8.40pm on 24 February after
OL,20,Freceiving a call about the two men
OL,21,F"acting suspiciously".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
