OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FA statement from the mosque said
OL,7,Fvolunteers "spotted a suspicious bag"
OL,8,Fbefore approaching and challenging one
OL,9,Fof the men, described as white in his
OL,10,F50s. He was accompanied by another
OL,11,Fman, a black male, it added.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) has
OL,14,Fconfirmed it is not treating the
OL,15,Fincident as terror-related - although
OL,16,Fofficers say they are working with
OL,17,FCounter Terrorism Policing North West.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FA man in his 50s has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of carrying an offensive
OL,8,Fweapon and possession of class B
OL,9,Fdrugs, and remains in custody for
OL,10,Fquestioning, the force said.
OL,12,FA search is underway to locate a
OL,13,Fsecond man, who is black, in his late
OL,14,F40s with an athletic build and short
OL,15,Fstubbled facial hair.
OL,17,FNo threats were made and nobody was
OL,18,Finjured, GMP added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FSpeaking at Prime Minister's
OL,7,FQuestions, Sir Keir Starmer said he
OL,8,Fshared the "deep concern of the
OL,9,Fcommunity" over the incident.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Manchester Central
OL,12,FMosque said a "serious security
OL,13,Fincident" had occurred during prayers.
OL,15,F"Mosque volunteers spotted the
OL,16,Fsuspicious bag containing an axe,
OL,17,Fwhich was placed into the main hall"
OL,18,Fbefore volunteers "escorted" a man
OL,19,Finto another room and found "multiple
OL,20,Fweapons including a hammer and a
OL,21,Fknife".
OL,26,@tD@OOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FA second man left before officers
OL,7,Farrived, the Mosque added, and all
OL,8,FCCTV has been provided to police.
OL,10,F"The Muslim community in the UK has
OL,11,Fexperienced a notable rise in threats
OL,12,Fand hostility over recent years," the
OL,13,FMosque said.
OL,15,F"The increase in Islamophobic
OL,16,Fincidents is a serious concern, and
OL,17,Fgreater resources are urgently needed
OL,18,Fto address this growing and real risk.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,F"We will continue to cooperate fully
OL,7,Fwith the police and urge all mosque
OL,8,Fattendees to remain vigilant.
OL,10,F"Congregants are advised to travel in
OL,11,Fgroups where possible and to ensure
OL,12,Fthat children are not left unattended.
OL,14,F"The swift and responsible actions of
OL,15,Four volunteers played a crucial role
OL,16,Fin containing the situation. Without
OL,17,Ftheir intervention, the consequences
OL,18,Fcould have been far more serious."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FGMP says the men had claimed to be in
OL,7,Fthe mosque to do work on the building
OL,8,F- which staff were unaware of.
OL,10,F"We're questioning a suspect in
OL,11,Fcustody after weapons were found on a
OL,12,Fman at Manchester Central Mosque last
OL,13,Fnight," Assistant Chief Constable John
OL,14,FWebster said.
OL,16,F"We were called at around 8.40pm to
OL,17,Fconcern from security staff at the
OL,18,Fmosque about a white man in a high-viz
OL,19,Fjacket carrying a bag with an axe
OL,20,Finside.
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,F"The man had reportedly claimed to be
OL,7,Fin the mosque to do work on the
OL,8,Fbuilding, but staff had no knowledge
OL,9,Fof this. They rightly acted on their
OL,10,Fsuspicions and called police.
OL,12,F"There was no suggestion that he made
OL,13,Fany threats or confronted members of
OL,14,Fthe congregation. However, we
OL,15,Funderstand the concern that this
OL,16,Fsuspicious and concerning behaviour
OL,17,Fcaused."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,FOfficers are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fto help with enquiries and have asked
OL,8,Fanyone with information to contact GMP
OL,9,Fon 101 or via the LiveChat function on
OL,10,Four website.
OL,12,FAlternatively, contact Crimestoppers
OL,13,Fon 0800 555 111.
OL,15,FAfzal Khan, the local MP for Rusholme,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I am deeply concerned about the
OL,17,Fincident that occurred at Manchester
OL,18,FCentral Mosque last night, whereby two
OL,19,Findividuals entered the mosque with
OL,20,Fweapons.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,F"Thankfully, everyone is safe, no one
OL,7,Fis hurt, and Greater Manchester Police
OL,8,Fhave arrested one of the suspects.
OL,10,F"I'm in touch with the mosque
OL,11,Fleadership, the Mayor of Greater
OL,12,FManchester, and the Prime Minister
OL,13,Fabout this incident.
OL,15,F"Just this week, the Chancellor and
OL,16,FHome Secretary announced more funding
OL,17,Ffor protecting mosques, and this
OL,18,Fincident demonstrates once again why
OL,19,Fthis funding is so vital.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772129063
OL,3,CMan arrested after allegedly entering
OL,4,Cmosque 'carrying multiple weapons'
OL,6,F"This is the consequence of far-right
OL,7,Fpoliticians scapegoating Muslims. This
OL,8,Fis Islamophobia, plain and simple."
OL,10,FIn a statement the Prime Minister
OL,11,Fsaid: "I am concerned to hear of the
OL,12,Fincident at Manchester Central Mosque
OL,13,Flast night. I know this will be
OL,14,Fworrying for Muslim communities,
OL,15,Fespecially during Ramadan, a time of
OL,16,Fpeace and reflection.
OL,18,F"My thanks go to the volunteers and
OL,19,Femergency services for their quick
OL,20,Fresponse."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
